OL,3,CShark among 81 species found along
OL,4,CSussex coastline by researchers
OL,6,FScientists from the University of
OL,7,FSussex have identified 81 different
OL,8,Fmarine species along the Sussex
OL,9,Fcoastline, including the tope shark
OL,10,Fand the European eel, which are both
OL,11,Fcritically endangered.
OL,13,FThey found the different creatures
OL,14,Fliving under the water across 28
OL,15,Fsurvey sites between Shoreham-by-Sea
OL,16,Fand Selsey, which also includes a 300-
OL,17,Fsquare kilometre area of local
OL,18,Fcoastline where a trawling ban was put
OL,19,Fin place in 2021.
