OL,6,FThe researchers said that while these
OL,7,Fspecies are not unique to UK waters,
OL,8,Fsome of them "are quite rare and of
OL,9,Fhigh conservation concern".
OL,11,FAlice Clark, a PhD candidate at the
OL,12,Funiversity, said: "Coastal ecosystems
OL,13,Fsuffer from a range of stressors
OL,14,Fincluding overfishing, habitat
OL,15,Fdegradation, pollution and climate
OL,16,Fchange, all of which can lead to
OL,17,Fpopulation decline and a loss of
OL,18,Fdiversity in species.
