OL,6,F"Through this analysis, we have been
OL,7,Fable to discover so many different
OL,8,Fspecies in our waters, and I think
OL,9,Fpeople will be surprised to learn just
OL,10,Fhow diverse this area of the UK
OL,11,Fcoastline is."
OL,13,FA Nearshore Trawling by-law was
OL,14,Fintroduced in March 2021 to prevent
OL,15,Ftrawlers from dredging in the near
OL,16,Finshore waters off the Sussex coast,
OL,17,Fwith the aim of providing an
OL,18,Fopportunity for kelp ecosystems and
OL,19,Fnative fish to recover.
