OL,6,FSince the ban was imposed, the team
OL,7,Fhas been conducting in-depth research
OL,8,Fto monitor underwater habitats and
OL,9,Fidentify the species that live along
OL,10,Fthe Sussex Bay.
OL,12,FAs well as the tope shark and the
OL,13,FEuropean eel, other species identified
OL,14,Fby researchers include the black
OL,15,Fseabream, the Atlantic mackerel, the
OL,16,Ftub gurnard fish, the cat shark and
OL,17,Fthe spotted ray.
