OL,6,FThe researchers say their work
OL,7,Fprovides a monitoring baseline of
OL,8,Fmarine life diversity in Sussex, and
OL,9,Fcould also help impact future
OL,10,Fconservation efforts around the globe.
OL,12,FMika Peck, professor of conservation
OL,13,Fecology at the University of Sussex
OL,14,Fand project co-lead, said: "There is
OL,15,Fthe urgent need to address destructive
OL,16,Ffishing practices globally.
OL,18,F"The seminal trawler ban by Sussex
OL,19,FIFCA (Inshore Fisheries & Conservation
OL,20,FAuthority) in 2021 being a leading
OL,21,Fexample.
