OL,6,F"Our team at Sussex are providing the
OL,7,Fcritical evidence to understand
OL,8,Fecosystem recovery upon removing human
OL,9,Fpressures, such as trawling, using
OL,10,Femerging technologies such as eDNA."
OL,12,FDr Valentina Scarponi, lecturer in
OL,13,Fecology and animal biology at the
OL,14,FUniversity of Sussex ` who also co-led
OL,15,Fthe project, added: "This is a very
OL,16,Fexciting project, as it will allow us
OL,17,Fto closely monitor changes in the
OL,18,Flocal marine community.
OL,20,F"We are very proud to be contributing
OL,21,Fto practical conservation efforts."
